			          		<div class="sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12" data-layout-label="Header Content" data-type="block-field" data-updated-on="1447278649518" id="blocks-content-header-privacy"><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-12 span-12"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-5163358882e0b50131b5"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h1 class="text-align-center">Privacy Policy</h1><p class="text-align-center">Bandsintown, LLC</p></div></div></div></div></div>
